# Products API

This project is a REST API built with Node.js, Express, TypeScript, MongoDB (Mongoose), and Swagger.
It implements full CRUD functionality for managing products and is deployed to Vercel.

---

## ðŸ“¦ Features

- Create, read, update, and delete products
- MongoDB Atlas cloud database
- Input validation and error handling
- Rate limiting to protect API endpoints
- Interactive API documentation using Swagger

---

## ðŸ§± Tech Stack

- Node.js
- Express
- TypeScript
- MongoDB Atlas + Mongoose
- Swagger (swagger-jsdoc & swagger-ui-express)
- Vercel (deployment)

---

## ðŸ“Œ API Endpoints

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|------|--------|------------|
| POST | `/api/v1/products` | Create a new product |
| GET | `/api/v1/products` | Retrieve all products |
| GET | `/api/v1/products/:id` | Retrieve a product by ID |
| PUT | `/api/v1/products/:id` | Update a product by ID |
| DELETE | `/api/v1/products/:id` | Delete a product by ID |
